    "description": "Complete test collection for auth-service endpoints via API Gateway (port 8080).\n\nSetup:\n1. Login via POST /api/v1/auth/login\n2. The test script auto-saves the token to the `accessToken` collection variable.\n3. All protected endpoints automatically use {{accessToken}}.",
